headline: U.S. tower stock valuations refreshed at MoffettNathanson
summary: Investing.com -- MoffettNathanson analysts refreshed their valuations for U.S. tower companies following recent industry developments, including strong year-to-date performance and Crown Castle’s sale of its Fiber business.
